    <div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > PLAYISM [348 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/playism">PLAYISM</a> and developer Nigoro have will release a free update for slap battle <a title="Genres > Action [3,445 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/genres/action">action game</a> <em><a title="Games > Rose &amp; Camellia Collection" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/rose-camellia-collection">Rose &amp; Camellia Collection</a></em> in June that adds an online battle mode, the companies announced. <span id="more-1046805"></span></p><p><em>Rose &amp; Camellia Collection</em> is available now for <a title="Platforms > Switch [18,382 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>.</p><p>Watch a new trailer below.</p><h2><span>“Online Battle Mode” Update Announce Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="『薔薇と椿 ～お豪華絢爛版～』オンラインお対決モヲド～お電波通信対戦編～ 告知トレーラー" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/oMl7uUT7ZCc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
